{"metadata":{"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"setUser:emails:"}],"modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"symbolKind":"method","roleHeading":"Type Method","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)setUser:emails:","title":"setUser:emails:","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"text":"setUser:emails:","kind":"identifier"}]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setUser:emails:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setUser:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString","text":"NSString"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"userId","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"emails:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"NSArray","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSArray"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"text":"emails","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}]},{"parameters":[{"name":"userId","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The custom user identifier."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"emails","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Array of email address strings to associate with the user.","type":"text"}]}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Convenience method that combines "},{"code":"setUserId:","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"code":"setEmails:","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" into a single"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"server request. This is more efficient than calling both methods separately","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"and ensures atomic association of user ID with emails."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use this during login or registration flows when you have both user ID"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"and email available simultaneously."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"text":"Example","type":"heading","anchor":"Example"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Complete registration with user ID and emails:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["class RegistrationManager {","","    func completeRegistration(_ registration: RegistrationData) {","        \/\/ Create user on backend","        APIClient.shared.createUser(registration) { result in","            guard case .success(let user) = result else { return }","","            \/\/ Set both user ID and emails in single operation","            var emails = [user.email]","            if let secondaryEmail = registration.secondaryEmail {","                emails.append(secondaryEmail)","            }","","            Pushwoosh.configure.setUser(user.id, emails: emails)","","            \/\/ Set initial user tags","            Pushwoosh.configure.setTags([","                \"registration_date\": ISO8601DateFormatter().string(from: Date()),","                \"registration_source\": registration.source.rawValue,","                \"account_type\": user.accountType.rawValue,","                \"has_completed_onboarding\": false","            ])","        }","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":null,"code":["   when you need confirmation."]}],"kind":"content"}],"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setuser:emails:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"abstract":[{"text":"Sets user identifier and emails together in a single operation.","type":"text"}],"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"title":"PushwooshCore","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","type":"topic","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"abstract":[],"type":"topic","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","title":"PWConfiguration","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"PWConfiguration"}],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/setUser:emails:":{"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setUser:emails:"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"setUser:emails:"}],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setuser:emails:","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setUser:emails:","abstract":[{"text":"Sets user identifier and emails together in a single operation.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","title":"setUser:emails:","role":"symbol"}}}